Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你能聽到我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼發生的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我與你之間可能隔著千山萬水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could be thousands of miles away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 只要你打開你的設備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and yet, when you turn on whatever device
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的聲音和圖像就會傳到你那裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is bringing my image and voice to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在這裏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有任何的間斷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切是如何變成現實的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對於我們的祖先來說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To our ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切看起來就像是魔法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it would've seemed like sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對他們來說,信息傳播的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For them, speed of communication
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,取決於快馬的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was only as fast as the swiftest horse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,或是航船的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or sailing ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現代社會的信息以肉眼不可見的光速進行傳播\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our messages travel invisibly at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是如何獲得如此不可思議的力量的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did we attain such mythic powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這一切都來源於一個人的頭腦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It all began in the mind of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一個貧民家的小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A child of poverty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,聽起來沒什麼可期待的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of whom nothing was expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可要是沒有這個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, if this man had not lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在的世界也許就不會是這個樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the world we know might not exist today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,中文翻譯 幸福的微笑 timhal
